Amouranth:

Kaitlyn Siragusa (born December 2, 1993), better known as Amouranth (pronounced as "amaranth"), is an American Internet celebrity, streamer, and OnlyFans model. Siragusa is also known for her ASMR Twitch livestreams.

Siragusa was initially a cosplayer, appearing at character parties for children and doing hospital visits. In 2016, she was asked by streaming company Twitch to join as a content creator and livestream making costumes. She accepted, and by 2021, became the most popular female streamer on Twitch, known for her dancing, ASMR, and hot tub streaming content.
